peopleAlsoAsk.question: How do you appraise old currency?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Hire a professional appraiser to grade your coins and tell you how much it is worth. The American Society of Appraisers and International Society of Appraisers have searchable directories of professional appraisers. A dealer might also be able to help.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: Is my old foreign currency worth anything?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Most foreign coins aren't worth more than their face value, but old (more than 100 years old) and rare coins could be worth a lot of money. And just like domestic coins, the condition of the foreign coin is of paramount importance.
